{{root|en|ine-pro|*kʷyeh₁-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|requiem}}, from {{der|en|la|requiem}}, the first word of the [[introit]] for the traditional requiem mass, an alternative [[accusative case]] of {{der|en|la|requiēs||rest, repose}}, from {{m|la|re-||again}} + {{m|la|quiēs||rest, quiet}}.

